---
title: One-Pot Mexican-Style Pork Stew with Tortilla Chips
description: Packed with hearty and delicious pork and veggies, this Mexican stew is the perfect remedy to a long work week. Crushed tortilla chips and a dollop of sour cream offer a pop of flavour to top it all off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-mexican-style-pork-stew-d46e5b23.jpg
